text: Western Sydney Wanderers F.C. is an Australian professional soccer club from Western Sydney, New South Wales. It competes in the A-League, under license from Football Federation Australia (FFA). ==Honours== *AFC Champions League :Champions (1): 2014 *A-League :Premiers (1): 2012–13 :Runners-up (1): 2013–14 *A-League Finals :Runners-up (2): 2013, 2014 ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:A-League Men
title: Western Sydney Wanderers FC
